{"type":"article","id":3850,"title":"民国时期中国富人学生和现在中国富人学生的对比","uid":8751,"topics":[158,147,153,163,161,26,17,16,2143],"contents":"大家不妨看看民国时期中国的富人和学生：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/NnIQcBH.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NnIQcBH.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NnIQcBH.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/jjR50IB.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jjR50IB.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jjR50IB.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/3a28QHi.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3a28QHi.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/3a28QHi.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hImlSn4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hImlSn4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hImlSn4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/nzp7wdg.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/nzp7wdg.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/nzp7wdg.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Yu4PElh.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Yu4PElh.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Yu4PElh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/a7omT8A.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a7omT8A.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/a7omT8A.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlEg8dt.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlEg8dt.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/zlEg8dt.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n在民国时候，虽然战火纷飞，硝烟弥漫，中国富人和学生基本上都是特别的有素养，举止说话行为得体大方优雅，就连外国人都称赞我们特别文明。我曾经听到这样的一个故事：民国时候有开着福特车的富人和富人太太遇到行人的时候主动礼让行人，让行人先走。这件事至今都令人汗颜<br>\n再看看现在中国的富人和学生：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/PYoG8nI.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PYoG8nI.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/PYoG8nI.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7w5uB4k.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7w5uB4k.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/7w5uB4k.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LiWLF0v.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LiWLF0v.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LiWLF0v.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRmFba0.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRmFba0.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/rRmFba0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHy8z0l.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHy8z0l.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gHy8z0l.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/IRTdyQ3.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IRTdyQ3.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/IRTdyQ3.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n现在的中国富人和学生，大部分行为都非常出鲁，尤其是海外留学生，简直出鲁恶心到了无法形容的地步，还动不动就开豪车，打人，还对反送中的港人说“cnmb”、“穷逼”等恶心不堪入目到无法用人类语言形容的话语，真是无语……<br>\n赵国战狼粉红留学生一方面花着赵国纳税人的钱，干着不是人干的事，另一方面却是赵家人不用纳税人的钱投资贫困山区的教育。诶！今日中国教育，连民国都比不上，算是彻底完了！<br>\n诶!现在的中国富人学生，跟民国时候的中国富人学生，真不是一个档次的人!","date":"2019-08-23","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}